name: "Over Under Around + Thru" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Brush pen and paint pen on paper with digital embellishments and color.] I'm going to plead the 5th on this one. (I don't want to incriminate myself...) The words are "borrowed," not stolen, from a kids' book I read when I was little... The image is a self-portrait (in a psychological sense.) Enjoy!!! ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
